text: Xie Jiaxuan (; ; born 30 August 1994) is a Chinese speed skater who competes internationally. He participated at the 2018 Winter Olympics and competed in the men's 500m event finishing on 31st position. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of China Category:Speed skaters at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Speed skaters at the 2017 Asian Winter Games
